You're not hurting anyone!

18:50.088 --> 18:51.712
It's a utopia.

18:51.714 --> 18:53.464
No, a me-topia!

18:53.466 --> 18:57.218
Yes, well, you don't really want
everyone to be like you.

18:57.220 --> 18:59.971
Earth-shattering reveal!

18:59.973 --> 19:01.097
[screaming]

19:01.099 --> 19:02.515
[chuckling à la homer]

