When did insurance commercials
get so funny?

19:06.062 --> 19:08.354
[gasps] marge!

19:08.356 --> 19:10.356
Cooperating with us
is the only way

19:10.358 --> 19:12.942
To get your wife back to normal.

19:12.944 --> 19:16.362
